 tryed to finish him by kiting.  Managed to kill him, but the manacrafter instilled me before I could charm him. :P  Dead again.  With time against me, I still managed to run from plane of knowledge back in time to loot my belt (dropped first time).  Having only memmed speed song, I hauled arse, dragging my corpse, before more than 2 could aggro me, only pausing to get my drum.  Now I have 11% more haste, and I'll try getting to the assassin in guk again : ) (already got the mask, really going for the bag)</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Dont make me drive by punch ye druid!<br/>Longtounge Speedmyster<br/>52 Bard of Xegony<br/><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=347604" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=347604</a></td></tr>
